<SUMMARY>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=2 -->
SUMMARY: 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
The Coast Guard is establishing a safety zone on the Upper Mississippi River. This regulation is needed to control
vessel traffic in the regulated area to provide safe working conditions and navigation within the affected area.
The regulation will prohibit navigation in the regulated area for the safety of vessel traffic and the protection
of life and property associated with bridge and span removal.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
</SUMMARY>
