<SUMMARY>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=2 -->
SUMMARY: 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
The Coast Guard is establishing a safety zone on the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Youghiogheny River from mile 0.8 to mile 1.8. This regulation is 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
needed to control vessel traffic in the regulated area during 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
demolition of the main span of a bridge at mile 1.3. This 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
regulation will restrict general navigation in the regulated area 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
during demolition and subsequent debris clearing operations for 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the safety of vessels transitting the area.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
</SUMMARY>
