<SUMMARY>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=2 -->
SUMMARY:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
 This rule issues technical amendments to Medicare 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
regulations intended to simplify and improve our system for 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
evaluating the performance of fiscal intermediaries and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
carriers in the administration of the Medicare program. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Currently, we evaluate intermediaries using performance 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
criteria and standards announced in an annual notice in the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=4 -->
Federal Register
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
. We are clarifying the methodology for 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
establishing these criteria and standards. For consistency, 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
we establish comparable regulation requirements for the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
evaluation of carrier performance. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
These revisions are published in accordance with 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
sections 1816(f) and 1842(b)(2) of the Social Security Act 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
which require us to develop standards, criteria, and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
procedures to evaluate an intermediary's or carrier's 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
overall performance.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
</SUMMARY>
