<!-- PJG ITAG l=09 g=2 f=1 -->
h
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=09 g=1 f=1 -->
Only jack mackerel caught north of 39
<!-- PJG 0017 degreeslatlong -->
&cir;00
<!-- PJG 0020 minuteslatlong -->
&rsquo; N. latitude are governed by the FMP. The ABC and harvest guideline also include area beyond 200 nm.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

