a valid limited-entry permit issued under 50 CFR part 663 for trawl gear, and (ii) all fishing on the trip takes place
south of Point Arena and the landing includes California halibut of a size required at California Fish and Game Code
Section 8392(a) which states:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 04 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=1 -->
