) are satisfied by each program. Any such degree program shall be, at a minimum, either through an accredited community
college (leading to an associate's degree), 4-year college (a bachelor's degree), or diploma school, and the course
of study shall be one accredited by a State Board of Nursing (or its equivalent). For career ladder or career path programs,
the facility shall maintain documentation that the programs are normally part of a course of study or training which
