<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Merit, education, and specialty.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 For salary advancement based on factors such as merit, education, and specialty, the facility shall maintain and
make available for inspection documentation that it provides opportunities for professional development of its
nurses which lead to salary advancement, 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
e.g.
