 (A) The individual is enrolled in, participating in, or has successfully completed a job search program which meets
the requirements of &sect;617.49(a); or the State agency has determined that no acceptable job search program is
reasonably available under the criteria set forth in &sect;617.49(c). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
