of the following requirements of paragraphs (a)(2) (i) through (vii) of this section: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(i) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Certification. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

