law or plan of a State or the United States, or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
iii
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
) Had adversely affected employment interrupted to serve as a full-time representative of a labor organization in
such firm or subdivision, or 
