(
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
iv
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
) Is on call-up for the purpose of active duty in a reserve status in the Armed Forces of the United States (if such week
began after August 1, 1990), provided such active duty is ``Federal service'' as defined in part 614 of this chapter,

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
shall be treated as a week of employment at wages of $30 or more; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

