<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(A) The individual must_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
1
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
) Be enrolled in or participating in a training program approved pursuant to &sect;617.22(a), or 
