&sect;617.64 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Termination of TAA program benefits. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The following rules are applicable to the termination of TAA benefits under the Act: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(a) No application for TRA, or transportation or subsistence payment while in training approved under subpart C of
this part 617, shall be approved, and no payment of TRA or payment for transportation or subsistence occurring on or
before the termination date shall be made after the termination date specified in the Act, unless the claim for TRA
